'''米哈伊尔·瓦西里耶维奇·伊格纳季耶夫'''（{{lang-ru|Михаи́л Васи́льевич Игна́тьев}}，{{lang-cv|Михал Ваçлин ывăл Йăкăнатьев}}，{{bd|1962年|1月8日|2020年|6月18日|catIdx=Ignatyev}}），[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]政治家。他於2010年8月28日當選[[楚瓦什共和國|楚瓦什共和國]]第二任總統，並於翌日正式就任。<ref>{{Cite news |date=18 June 2020 |title=Cheboksary. Chuvashia. On Sunday, August 29, Mikhail Ignatiev will officially take office as President of Chuvashia. |url=https://susanin.news/udmurtia/power/20100829-68878/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200620224910/https://susanin.news/udmurtia/power/20100829-68878/ |archive-date=20 June 2020 |access-date=20 June 2020 }}</ref>2012年1月1日，楚瓦什共和國總統這一職位被更名為楚瓦什共和國首腦。2015年6月9日，他結束第一次任期，被俄羅斯總統[[弗拉基米尔·普京|弗拉基米尔·普京]]任命為代理首腦，隨後他於9月13日成功連任。<ref>{{Cite news |date=18 June 2020 |title=Ex-head of Chuvashia Mikhail Ignatiev died of coronavirus |work=[[Interfax|Interfax]] |url=https://www.interfax.ru/russia/713807 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200620222429/https://www.interfax.ru/russia/713807 |archive-date=20 June 2020 |access-date=18 June 2020 }}</ref>

2020年1月18日，伊格纳季耶夫在國家新聞日的致辭上呼籲「消滅」批評政府的記者。<ref name="life">{{Cite news |date=24 January 2020 |title=Jump for it Russian governor draws criticism for forcing firefighter to leap for keys to new fire-engine |work=[[Meduza|Meduza]] |url=https://meduza.io/en/feature/2020/01/24/jump-for-it |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200620215328/https://meduza.io/en/feature/2020/01/24/jump-for-it |archive-date=20 June 2020 |access-date=18 June 2020 }}</ref>

1月28日，他被[[統一俄羅斯黨|統一俄羅斯黨]]開除黨籍。翌日，普京罷免他的首腦職務，由{{link-ru|奧列格·阿列克謝耶維奇·尼古拉耶夫|Николаев, Олег Алексеевич|奧列格·尼古拉耶夫}}代行職權。<ref>{{Cite news |date=29 January 2020 |title=Putin Sacks Russian Governor Over Key-Dangling Video |work=[[The_Moscow_Times|The Moscow Times]] |url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/01/29/putin-sacks-russian-governor-over-key-dangling-video-a69056 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200620221228/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/01/29/putin-sacks-russian-governor-over-key-dangling-video-a69056 |archive-date=20 June 2020 |access-date=20 June 2020 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |date=29 January 2020 |title=Putin dismissed the head of Chuvashia "in connection with the loss of confidence" |work=[[Interfax|Interfax]] |url=https://www.interfax.ru/russia/693222 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200620221439/https://www.interfax.ru/russia/693222 |archive-date=20 June 2020 |access-date=20 June 2020 }}</ref>5月20日，他認為普京的解職行為涉嫌違法，向俄羅斯最高法院提起訴訟。他的訴訟於5月21日獲得接受，預計於6月30日舉行現場聽證會。<ref>{{Cite news |date=27 May 2020 |title=Scandal-Plagued Ex-Governor Sues Putin for Wrongful Dismissal |work=[[The_Moscow_Times|The Moscow Times]] |url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/05/27/scandal-plagued-ex-governor-sues-putin-for-wrongful-dismissal-a70393 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200620220340/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/05/27/scandal-plagued-ex-governor-sues-putin-for-wrongful-dismissal-a70393 |archive-date=20 June 2020 |access-date=20 June 2020 }}</ref>然而在5月27日，他因雙側肺炎住院，肺部大面積受損。<ref>{{Cite news |date=27 May 2020 |title=Ex-head of Chuvashia Ignatiev hospitalized with bilateral pneumonia |work=[[Kommersant|Kommersant]] |url=https://www.kommersant.ru/doc/4357499?tg |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200620220616/https://www.kommersant.ru/doc/4357499?tg |archive-date=20 June 2020 |access-date=20 June 2020 }}</ref>6月18日，伊格纳季耶夫在感染[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]後，因心力衰竭在[[聖彼得堡|聖彼得堡]]一家醫院死亡。<ref>{{Cite news |date=19 June 2020 |title=Ex-Governor Who Sued Putin Dies From Coronavirus – Reports |work=[[The_Moscow_Times|The Moscow Times]] |url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/06/19/ex-governor-who-sued-putin-dies-from-coronavirus-reports-a70629 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200620221738/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/06/19/ex-governor-who-sued-putin-dies-from-coronavirus-reports-a70629 |archive-date=20 June 2020 |access-date=20 June 2020 }}</ref>

